626. Exchange Seats

Input: 
Seat table:
+----+---------+
| id | student |
+----+---------+
| 1  | Abbot   |
| 2  | Doris   |
| 3  | Emerson |
| 4  | Green   |
| 5  | Jeames  |
+----+---------+

select 
(Case when MOD(ID%2 <> 0 and id = (select max(id) from seat) then id
     when MOD(ID%2<>0 then id+1 
     else id-1
 end) as  id, student
from seat 
order by id;

